  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Describe how to set up a boundary-value problem for the stationary Schr&#1255;dinger equation</item> 
<item>Explain why the energy of a quantum particle in a box is quantized</item>
<item>Describe the physical meaning of stationary solutions to Schr&#1255;dinger&#8217;s equation and the connection of these solutions with time-dependent quantum states</item>
<item>Explain the physical meaning of Bohr&#8217;s correspondence principle</item>
</list></md:abstract>
